			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Cutting fabric straight is an essential skill for professional-looking results in sewing projects. There are various methods to do it, including using a fabric calculator, fussy cutting, planning your patchwork, and using a ruler and rotary cutter. The fabric's grain lines should be checked to ensure the cut edges are perfectly straight. This can be done by pulling out a thread and using the empty gap to cut it straight, or making a 2″ cut and ripping the rest of the fabric.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">要想在缝纫项目中做出专业的效果，直剪布料是一项基本技能。有多种方法可以做到这一点，包括使用布料计算器、挑剔裁剪、规划拼接以及使用尺子和圆盘转刀。应检查布料的纹理线，确保裁剪的边缘完全平直。具体做法是：拉出一条线，利用空隙将其剪直，或者剪开 2 英寸的口子，然后撕开其余的布料。</common:generalComment>
